snippet.title: AILA Gameplay Reactions - Convergence Showcase
snippet.description:
Some "highlights" of five creators playing through the terrifying opening of first-person horror AILA from Pulsatrix Studios and Fireshine Games, as revealed in Convergence Showcase. Wishlist it today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2695430

Starring:
Marignetic - @marignetic 
Riley Scallon - @RileyScallon 
Aeroga - @Aeroga 
Vivid Discord - https://www.tiktok.com/@vivid_discord
MrKravin - @MrKravin

#convergenceshow #indiegame
